JS6LZ5Jo0w">Trần Hiến Chương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Thu%E1%BB%B7-ti%C3%AAn/poem-qp9xmpY0dTIIV6ZA8AVRxg">Thuỷ tiên - 水仙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-zD7mrwO-43MIHObHTaGOMw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh tự - 送尚書柴莊卿序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/author-1_5YGABQESnAmYdOvhbEZQ">Lý Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Vi%C3%AAn-quan-t%E1%BB%91ng-th%C3%A1i/poem-38aRwBtA56wskmwWwqZlCA">Viên quan tống thái - 園官送菜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Y%E1%BA%BFt-Ti%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BB%A7-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-S-d6JOz9cG49AGGWNxEDyA">Yết Tiên Chủ miếu - 謁先主廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
